    <item>
      <title>非政府组织称前往巴黎的俄罗斯运动员违反了国际奥委会的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russian-athletes-headed-to-paris-break-ioc-rules-and-sponsors-must-act-says-ngo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人权组织称，获准参加巴黎奥运会的俄罗斯和白俄罗斯运动员中有超过一半与军事机构有联系或支持乌克兰战争，该组织敦促奥运会赞助商进行干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russian-athletes-headed-to-paris-break-ioc-rules-and-sponsors-must-act-says-ngo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默与特朗普、万斯开启重启欧洲之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-starts-uk-reset-with-europe-as-trump-and-vance-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默在整个英国竞选活动中承诺要重塑因英国脱欧而恶化的欧洲关系。上任仅两周，他就全身心投入到这一努力中，在温斯顿·丘吉尔的祖屋接待了 40 多位欧洲大陆的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-starts-uk-reset-with-europe-as-trump-and-vance-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
